150
00:20:24,432 --> 00:20:25,432
<i>Pero luego...</i>

151
00:20:26,434 --> 00:20:27,526
<i>...que Dios nos ayude.</i>

152
00:20:28,352 --> 00:20:31,356
<i>La viuda, Babs.
Justo a tiempo.</i>

153
00:20:33,274 --> 00:20:34,274
Dios.

154
00:20:43,993 --> 00:20:44,993
Dios santo.

155
00:20:47,037 --> 00:20:49,005
¿Alguna vez te callas?

156
00:20:51,542 --> 00:20:54,445
No, no llores.

157
00:20:54,545 --> 00:20:56,889
Él no lo merece.

158
00:20:57,923 --> 00:20:58,923
